<title>DeathEvent</title><para>Published by <computeroutput>HealthUpdateSystem</computeroutput> when an entity dies. Contains:</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><computeroutput>source()</computeroutput> - Handle of the deceased entity</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput>attackContext()</computeroutput> - Optional combat context if death was from damage</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>Used by other systems (e.g., <computeroutput>CombatScoringSystem</computeroutput>) to react to entity deaths.</para>
